messages.ssml: <speak>The Center for Disease Control and Prevention reports that we do not know at this time if <sub alias="covid 19">COVID-19</sub> would cause problems during pregnancy or affect the health of the baby after birth. Pregnant women should do the same things as the general public to avoid infection.</speak>
